sections.heading: Proceedings, taxes or assessments levied, bonds issued; validity
sections.text: Any proceedings taken, taxes or assessments levied, or bonds issued pursuant to the Offstreet Parking District Act shall not be held invalid for failure to comply with the act.SourceLaws 1967, c. 60, ยง 5, p. 200;R.S.Supp.,1967, ยง 16-81
